WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.470
A Categorise slide turns sorting into a live quiz.

2
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:06.740
Click New Presentation to start a fresh deck.

3
00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:09.960
Your editor is loading — in a moment we'll pick the slide type.

4
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.360
Select Categorise from the slide type picker, in the Quiz section.

5
00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.620
Type your sorting challenge in the question field.

6
00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:19.570
Now add the items participants will sort.

7
00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:25.210
Enter the items, separated by commas — AhaSlides splits them automatically.

8
00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:31.350
Give your first category a name — this is the bucket they'll sort items into.

9
00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:34.670
Click Add Category to create as many buckets as you need.

10
00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:40.140
Your slide is ready — hit Present to go live with your audience.

11
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:46.620
Participants drag items into the right category on their phones — results appear on your screen in real time.

